To get the app running please follow the below setps

@root folder

npm install 
npm start

and you will be redirected to this landing page.

http://localhost:3000/login


The form fields errors/validations  are stored and retrieved  from the database considering easy maintenance , to avoid UI builds.

please check the server folder  and pdf to follow the instructions  to create a  user table to get the errors  Highlighted on UI

(server/util/validator.js ) --- shows the validation texts

also below are the  additional urls to route to


http://localhost:3000/signup

http://localhost:3000/products 


 


